2019-06-21  SVN: new release

	* Release: 0.9.30

2019-06-21 09:28  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* lcfg.yml, templates/debian/COMP-nagios.install,
	  templates/debian/COMP-nagios.manpages: list of default files for
	  nagios sub-package

2019-06-21 09:28  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* templates/debian/control: don't depend on perl if not a perl
	  component

2019-06-21 09:27  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* templates/debian/COMP.manpages: Only include manpages from
	  section 8 by default

2019-06-21 09:27  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* templates/debian/COMP.install: only include perl modules for
	  components by default

2019-06-21 09:27  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* lib/LCFG/Build/Tool/GenDeb.pm.in: Need Try::Tiny

2019-06-21 08:50  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* lcfg.yml, lib/LCFG/Build/Tool/GenDeb.pm.in: fixed logic for
	  nagios module check

2019-06-21 08:48  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* lib/LCFG/Build/Tool/GenDeb.pm.in,
	  templates/debian/COMP-nagios.install, templates/debian/control:
	  Added support for nagios sub-package for components

2019-06-20 09:54  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* Changes, debian/changelog, lcfg.yml: LCFG-Build-Tools release:
	  0.9.29

2019-06-20 09:54  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* debian/docs, debian/rules, lcfg.yml: Fixed installation of
	  changelog

2019-06-20 09:52  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* Changes, debian/changelog, lcfg.yml: LCFG-Build-Tools release:
	  0.9.28

2019-06-19 19:17  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* lib/LCFG/Build/Tool/GenDeb.pm.in: Handle changelog with
	  dh_installchangelogs rather than dh_install

2019-06-19 19:17  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* templates/debian/rules: Ensure upstream changelog is always
	  installed correctly

2019-04-17 08:29  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* Changes, debian/changelog, lcfg.yml: LCFG-Build-Tools release:
	  0.9.27

2019-04-16 09:06  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* templates/lcfg.cmake.tt: Removed debug message I didn't intend to
	  include

2019-04-16 09:04  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* templates/lcfg.cmake.tt: Handle case of distribution release
	  version not having a minor part (e.g. Centos), closes:
	  https://bugs.lcfg.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1129

2019-03-22 16:03  squinney@INF.ED.AC.UK

	* Changes, debian/changelog, lcfg.yml: LCFG-Build-Tools release:
	  0.9.26

